      "reviews": [
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Good quality",
          "reviewText": "This is a popular product for a reason and I won't be telling you anything new if you already saw someone review this. I am usually very worried about purchasing makeup on Amazon but my local drug stores don't seem to carry this line and I was really curious to try it so I took a chance. The product arrived fully sealed and is in good condition so I was very pleased by this. I managed to choose a good color match just based on the photos in the listing. I was looking for a more full coverage foundation for my aging skin. I have dry skin with oily t-zone so I have large pores in that area and a lot of foundations settle into pores and dry spots. This looks really nice on my skin even when I do have a few dry spots, and it works well with primer. I am very pleased to have an option when I do want full coverage foundation for an event or special occasion. I would probably exfoliate and super hydrate as part of the preparation to get the best look, of course. I am surprised by the longevity of this product, it has a satin-like finish rather than a full matte. I prefer a satin finish to either a matte finish or a glowy finish, so I was very happy. I am really fair and they have a lot of fair toned color options which you don't see a lot these days especially in a drugstore line. A little goes a long way so I appreciate that the pump dispenses the small amount at a time. Very easy to use and practical for long-term storage.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on April 4, 2024",
          "customer": "SandraKat",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AEVUTCN6HQMXWLBDB7WO4DXBO64Q",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
