            "size": "1 Fl Oz (Pack of 1)"
          },
          "helpfulVotes": "12 people found this helpful"
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Happy with my new foundation",
          "reviewText": "I\u2019ve been looking for a new foundation but picking a brand and color online is so hard and I can\u2019t believe I got it right with this one. It was in my cart for a while before i decided to buy. I spent time trying to figure out if I was cool, warm , or neutral. Honestly I\u2019m still not 100% but when checking online it seems like I\u2019m a deep winter with more neutral tones. Light olive in the winter and dark olive in the summer. Hopefully these details help someone else. Anyway I wound up choosing classic beige a shade on the end of the lighter neutrals and it\u2019s so close to my actual tone I couldn\u2019t have chosen better. I think In the summer I will def have to move to a medium neutral color like honey or something similar but I will figure it out and then update. Anyway no problems with breakouts as of yet like some have mentioned and my skin is very sensitive. I\u2019ve used it a handful of times and so far so good.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on March 20, 2026",
          "customer": "Dana Dee",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AG3MDLAS4V45YEERZJ5WBGJFQKSQ",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
