            "color": "CLASSIC BEIGE",
            "size": "1 Fl Oz (Pack of 1)"
          }
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Saved by Covergirl.. again",
          "reviewText": "I was very scared to try this product because I\u2019ve been loyal to Covergirl Clean but since it\u2019s been discontinued and the new formula just doesn\u2019t feel the same, I decided to branch out and try something new. This product is amazing. It blended seemingly and flawlessly. It\u2019s buildable as well. I usually like to be light with foundation but you can definitely get the coverage you want. The texture was creamy. Not watery at all. I will say to go a little lighter than usual with this product because it is darker and that\u2019s probably from it being a matte finish. I read comments before ordering and took it into consideration. I also had a friend who had to return to get a shade lighter. So by that information, I got the perfect color for my skin tone. I think this is a BANG for your buck! I will continue to use this from now on. Thank you Covergirl!! \ud83d\ude3c",
